nodes.text: Keene was a mercenary member of the Vrath Xizor's team in 3653 BBY for the purpose to track the smuggler Zeerid Korr. Keene was Vrath's speeder driver in his team and he picked up the survivors of the team after a skirmish that year. He, like the rest of the surviving team members were told to rendezvous on Ord Mantell in three days, although Xizor was killed before then.
